java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatt1005.foodi.model.objects.dtos.Ingredient

no.ntnu.idatt1005.foodi.model.objects.dtos.ExpiringIngredient
public class ExpiringIngredient extends AmountedIngredient
This class represents the amounted ingredient object with an expiration date. It extends the AmountedIngredient class and adds an expirationDate field.
